title: The Collected Jennifer Blood (2011-2013)
description:
"[...T]his is the story of Jennifer Blood: I kill people. I enjoy it."



Contains:

THE GARTH ENNIS ARC - "Jennifer Blood" issues 1 thru 6, compiled into a single pseudo-TPB for your convenience. Traditional releases from Minutemen-DTs.

THE AL EWING ARC - "Jennifer Blood" issues 7 thru 23, compiled into one. Digital Mixed-Res releases from Empire.

1965: MY FATHER, THE MONSTER - "Jennifer Blood" 24, a stand-alone prequel issue. Original Digital Hi-Res release from Nahga-Empire.

THE NINJETTES - Spin-off prequel, six issues compiled into one. Digital Lo-Res releases from Empire.

FIRST BLOOD - Yet another prequel, and again six issues compiled into one. Digital Mixed-Res releases from Nahga-Empire.

Excludes: Issues 25 thru 28, beginning a new arc - grab separately or wait for a future iteration of this collection.
